    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your focus allows you to smash your enemy's defenses.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Improved Unarmed Strike, Stunning Fist.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You can make a Stunning Fist attempt as a full-round action. If successful, instead of stunning your target, you reduce the target's AC by an amount equal to your Wisdom modifier for 1 minute. This penalty does not stack with other penalties applied due to Crushing Blow.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When using this feat, you can spend either 2 or 4 stamina points. If you do, the Crushing Blow attack reduces the target's AC by an additional 1 for every 2 stamina points you spent.",
